						               													<description>Red Water Depths is a campaign-driven expansion for Fire for Light that includes five new chapters. During each chapter, you set up a new scenario with new enemies and objectives. Most importantly, players are given choices that will change the outcome of their games and give them access to different rewards or shape future chapters differently.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Red Water Depths introduces the new Fire exposure, as well as new lava terrain, that will fundamentally change the environment. Inside you can also expect;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     5 new chapters in a new small Storybook&amp;#10;     new tokens&amp;#10;     new Foes&amp;#10;     new Item cards&amp;#10;     new Trait cards&amp;#10;     and so much more!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Red Water Depths introduces a whole new region inside a dark volcano where elves have claimed regency after slaying the dragon Arkunda! The Flame King is quickly extending his rule. The explorers must rally the people to defend themselves against an army of goblins and ogres before it's too late!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Make your choices and save the people in Red Water Depths!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
